      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient $\\alpha,\\beta,\\gamma \\in \\R$ tels que $\\alpha+\\beta+\\gamma = \\pi$.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\alpha,\\beta,\\gamma \\in\n\\R\\)</span> tels que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\alpha+\\beta+\\gamma =\n\\pi\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2959eda7-31d5-4501-a5f0-5bde53c7cd30",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Démontrer que : $1 - \\cos\\alpha + \\cos\\beta + \\cos\\gamma =\n                 4\\sin\\frac\\alpha2 \\cos\\frac\\beta2 \\cos\\frac\\gamma2$.",
        "html": "<p>Démontrer que : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(1 - \\cos\\alpha +\n\\cos\\beta + \\cos\\gamma =\n                 4\\sin\\frac\\alpha2 \\cos\\frac\\beta2\n\\cos\\frac\\gamma2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "953ab948-7f0d-4dc7-89c3-13e78e6c0235",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$1 - \\cos\\alpha = 2\\sin\\frac\\alpha2 \\cos\\frac {\\beta+\\gamma}2$,\n\n$\\cos\\beta + \\cos\\gamma = 2\\sin\\frac\\alpha2 \\cos\\frac {\\beta-\\gamma}2$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(1 - \\cos\\alpha = 2\\sin\\frac\\alpha2\n\\cos\\frac {\\beta+\\gamma}2\\)</span>,</p>\n<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\cos\\beta + \\cos\\gamma =\n2\\sin\\frac\\alpha2 \\cos\\frac {\\beta-\\gamma}2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
